    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This specialized EpFunc is for returning a single field value, but the field lookup requires an index argument as well. Unlike the regular <ref refid="classGetOpFunc" kindref="compound">GetOpFunc</ref>, this variant takes the <ref refid="classEref" kindref="compound">Eref</ref> and Qinfo. It generates an opFunc that takes a single argument: FuncId of the function on the object that requested the value. The EpFunc then sends back a message with the info. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
